 Nov 2024 11:05:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/guyanas-pick-new-us-startup-faces-hurdles-tap-vast-gas-reserves-2024-11-25/</guid></item><item><title>比亚迪称明年将推出新一代刀片电池</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/byd-says-it-will-launch-new-generation-blade-batteries-next-year-2024-11-25/</link><description>据中国官方媒体 CGTN 周六报道，中国电动汽车巨头比亚迪表示将于 2025 年推出新一代刀片电池。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 08:13:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/byd-says-it-will-launch-new-generation-blade-batteries-next-year-2024-11-25/</guid></item><item><title>中方希望日本在宣布免签后致力于改善人员往来</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-hopes-japan-works-towards-improved-people-exchanges-after-visa-free-2024-11-25/</link><description>在北京上周宣布对日本公民实行免签证安排后，中国表示希望日本努力改善两国人员往来。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 07:32:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-hopes-japan-works-towards-improved-people-exchanges-after-visa-free-2024-11-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国外交部长表示中国和欧盟不是对手</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-eu-are-not-adversaries-says-chinese-foreign-minister-2024-11-25/</link><description>中国外交部长王毅周一表示，中国和欧盟是伙伴而不是对手，呼吁双方站在对方角度思考、寻求合作。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 07:29:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-eu-are-not-adversaries-says-chinese-foreign-minister-2024-11-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国欢迎英伟达继续存在并承诺为外国企业提供更好的环境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-vice-commerce-minister-meets-with-nvidia-senior-executive-2024-11-25/</link><description>中国商务部副部长周一在北京举行的一次会议上对英伟达的一位高管表示，中国欢迎英伟达的存在，并致力于为外国企业营造更好的商业环境。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 06:40:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-vice-commerce-minister-meets-with-nvidia-senior-executive-2024-11-25/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：债券上涨，美元因国债选择而下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-11-25/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 05:32:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-11-25/</guid></item><item><title>美国财政部长消息称黄金因获利了结而下跌1%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-prices-ease-three-week-peak-profit-taking-2024-11-25/</link><description>金价周一下跌 1%，因投资者在五个交易日上涨至三周高点后获利了结，而基金经理斯科特·贝森特 (Scott Bessent) 宣布出任新任美国财政部长，抑制了避险买盘。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 03:09:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-prices-ease-three-week-peak-profit-taking-2024-11-25/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲足球周</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/week-asian-football-2024-11-25/</link><description>本周亚洲足球的谈话要点：</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 02:52:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/week-asian-football-2024-11-25/</guid></item><item><title>台湾六个月来首次报告中国气球</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-chinese-balloon-first-time-six-months-2024-11-25/</link><description>台湾国防部周一报告称，在台湾北部海域发现了一个中国气球，这是自四月份以来首次报告此类事件，台北认为这是北京骚扰模式的一部分。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 02:49:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-chinese-balloon-first-time-six-months-2024-11-25/</guid></item><item><title>IPO冻结促使投资者行使赎回权，中国初创企业遭受损失</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-startups-suffer-ipo-freeze-prompts-investors-exercise-redemption-rights-2024-11-25/</link><description>行业高管表示，由于未能在约定的时间内通过市场上市退出，中国初创企业越来越难以满足早期风险投资家要求返还投资或面临诉讼的要求。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 02:30:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-startups-suffer-ipo-freeze-prompts-investors-exercise-redemption-rights-2024-11-25/</guid></item><item><title>贝森特当选下一任美国财长，世界股市和债券反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-25/</link><description>周一，世界市场对基金经理斯科特·贝森特(Scott Bessent)当选美国财政部长表示欢迎，希望他能够限制债务水平，而收益率下降则打压美元，黄金和原油等大宗商品下跌。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 00:12:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国地方政府在袭击事件后加强公共安全措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-local-governments-step-up-public-safety-measures-after-attacks-2024-11-24/</link><description>据媒体周日报道，在发生几起备受瞩目的大规模杀戮事件后，中国地方当局正在加强安全管理和警察巡逻，中央政府呼吁加强公共安全。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Nov 2024 10:20:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-local-governments-step-up-public-safety-measures-after-attacks-2024-11-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>